- Create Virtual Environment
>python3 -m venv env (env is the virutal environment name)

- Activate Virtual Environment
>source env/bin/activate

- Install packages those will be used in the project. They will be available only for that project
>pip3 install bs4 requests (Both packages bs4 and requests, will be installed only in the Virtual Environment)

- Run the application
>python3 app.py

- To generate an executable file (using pyinstaller) need to copy library folder to the dist/app folder, then run from terminal > ./app
